Package: tg
Title: The Grammar of Tables
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Shawn", "Garbett", email = "shawn.garbett@vanderbilt.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Jennifer", "Thompson", email = "	jennifer.l.thompson@vanderbilt.edu", role= c("ctb"))
             )
Description: Provides an extensible formula system to quickly and easily create
    production quality tables. Each step of the process (with the exception of the
    grammar itself) is easily override by user functions. One can chose to override
    the generation of table elements, and bundles to achive New England Journal of
    Medicine and Hmisc behaviors are provided. Further rendering into a format is
    a separate step that can be override by a user as well, the package contains
    rendering for HTML5, LaTeX, Rmarkdown and an index format.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3), R6, stringr, base64enc, digest, magrittr
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
